WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:03.960
- You can combine models.

2
00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:06.450
I think it's also really
cool to think about

3
00:00:06.450 --> 00:00:07.980
how you combine those models, right?

4
00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:09.630
Like, when you can generate an image,

5
00:00:09.630 --> 00:00:11.700
what about bringing it to life with Veo?

6
00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:14.730
And then what about
creating a story around that

7
00:00:14.730 --> 00:00:16.740
using Gemini, passing
the video back to it.

8
00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:17.730
So, there's such a cool way

9
00:00:17.730 --> 00:00:19.410
to, like, chain all these things.

10
00:00:19.410 --> 00:00:21.900
And the cool thing about AI Studio also is

11
00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:23.340
you don't necessarily need to know

12
00:00:23.340 --> 00:00:24.750
how to chain those things.

13
00:00:24.750 --> 00:00:26.160
You just need to describe your idea.

14
00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:28.590
So, you could say, "I have the story.

15
00:00:28.590 --> 00:00:30.210
I want to imagine the storyboard.

16
00:00:30.210 --> 00:00:31.920
Then I want to animate that storyboard,"

17
00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:34.560
